cs.DB, cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.SE 

This paper is primarily focused on the theory and operations of relational databases, which falls under the category of cs.DB (Database). The paper also discusses the semantics of predicate calculus, which is related to cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper's focus on developing a mathematically adequate theory of relations and defining operations on relations could also be relevant to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
